Package emissary.kff

Class ChecksumResults

java.lang.Object
emissary.kff.ChecksumResults
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ChecksumResults extends Object implements Serializable
This class is a value object to store the results of both a CRC32 and a message digest computation.
